hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: I'm on a course at the moment boostultimate This trapeze style of dress is a great option for those fat days we all suffer from or if you've just had a nice big lunch. The copius amounts of fabric hang in an A-line, skimming the body and covering any lumps and bumps. And there are plenty of swing dresses to choose from if Linday's doesn't float your boat. Our favourite is the Free People dress (also previously seen on Britney Spears in yellow) or Topshop's upscale silk dress from their Boutique range.
